data.title: Susie Dietter on LinkedIn: An Oral History of ‘Godfellas,’ the Most Philosophical ‘Futurama’ Episode…
data.meta_description:
This is a fun interview I did about “Godfellas”, a Futurama episode I directed.

https://lnkd.in/gzRK5tSF
data.text:
Hey Everybody! I’ve recently rolled off directing on Beavis & Butthead season 3 (which was a total blast!) and returned from a relaxing vacay in northern Vermont and l’m now officially looking for a new opportunity! I’m available for directing and storyboard positions in both TV and Feature. Check out my portfolio on my LinkedIn profile!

I can FINALLY tell everyone OFFICIALLY that I have been working on BEAVIS & BUTTHEAD Season 3!!!!! These episodes are SO FUNNY I could hardly breathe and I hope you all tune in on COMEDY CENTRAL to check them out…because we really want to be picked up for a Season 4!!!! Oh…and…season 3 is wrapping up soon so if you’re looking for a kick ass director give me a holler!

I’m currently looking for new opportunities in directing and storyboard! Let me know if you are interested. Any help is greatly appreciated!

Hi everyone - I am looking for a new role and would appreciate your support. Thank you in advance for any connections, advice, or opportunities you can offer. #OpenToWork
